name: LESLAR Metaverse
description: LESLAR Metaverse is a cyber future themed digital world. Where every person in the metaverse can meet, communicate, play, work, and even compete virtually. Leslar Metaverse connects real-world businesses with the digital world creating a sustainable economic ecosystem. There are four main business pillars in Leslar Metaverse, which consist of gaming, staking, merchandising and education.
